summary: Working basement in Breezehome. Lots of boxes, lots of tools. Small space
descriptionHtml:
This mod makes a small basement in Breezehome.  

1 of each crafting table provided.
35 containers available to sort your stuff out, how you please. (If you can\'t do it in that number, you got issues close to me. :P  :)  )

Trapdoor takes you downstairs, in the alcove with the alchemy station
author: Pan Dragondagger --- aka -  Rex1029
